  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售系统的流程图，核心是顾客忠诚度模块。我想先放一个叫Retail_CustomerLoyalty的节点作为起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，起点是Retail_CustomerLoyalty。接下来它指向哪里？是整个流程的入口吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，顾客先进入忠诚度系统，然后流转到优惠券系统。所以Retail_CustomerLoyalty要连到Retail_CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Retail_CouponSystem节点，并建立了从Retail_CustomerLoyalty过来的连接。继续下一步？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "优惠券系统之后要对接收银终端，用Retail_PointOfSale这个节点。顾客在POS机上核销优惠券。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Retail_PointOfSale是收银终端的统称对吧？后面还有几个环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Retail_PointOfSale就是收银终端。后面还有两个环节，流程会再回到优惠券系统形成一个闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Retail_PointOfSale加上，并连好从Retail_CouponSystem过来的线。接下来是第二个Retail_PointOfSale节点吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要两个Retail_PointOfSale节点，表示收银流程的两个阶段。第一个POS节点连到第二个POS节点，然后第二个再连回Retail_CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加第二个Retail_PointOfSale，并完成了全部连接：CustomerLoyalty → CouponSystem → PointOfSale → PointOfSale → CouponSystem。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_CouponSystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，让我看一眼。两个POS节点名字一样会不会混淆？不过业务上确实都是收银终端，只是阶段不同。这样应该可以。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_PointOfSale",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Mermaid允许同名节点，系统内部会自动区分。整个流程是线性的从左到右，五个节点形成 Loyalty → Coupon → POS → POS → Coupon 的闭环结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个结构准确反映了我们的业务流程。顾客从忠诚度入口进来，经过优惠券核销，在POS完成两阶段处理，最后回到优惠券系统更新状态。可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "Retail_PointOfSale"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
